title: NASA astronaut hits halfway point of yearlong spaceflight - The Beaumont Enterprise
text:
In this Tuesday, Sept. 15, 2015 image made from video provided by NASA, astronauts Scott Kelly, left, and Kjell Lindgren, aboard the International Space Station, speak to actors from the movie "The Martian."
 The Beaumont Enterprise.
